rawberries to serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["For best results, ensure you have a thoroughly clean and dry mixing bowl before commencing step 3.","Decorate with any seasonal fruit of your choice (e.g. blueberries, mango, bananas).<br>","To ensure this recipe is gluten free, read the label of your cornflour. Some may contain traces of wheat or gluten.<br>"],"basicInfo":["advanced","5m","6h","10 portions"]}